{"id":101,"date":"2021-09-05T15:04:09","date_gmt":"2021-09-05T15:04:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/demo.diemvo.com\/?p=101"},"modified":"2021-09-05T15:04:09","modified_gmt":"2021-09-05T15:04:09","slug":"2-loai-tai-khoan-quang-cao-tiktok-ads-ban-nen-biet","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/baostar.pro\/2-loai-tai-khoan-quang-cao-tiktok-ads-ban-nen-biet\/","title":{"rendered":"2 Lo\u1ea1i T\u00e0i Kho\u1ea3n Qu\u1ea3ng C\u00e1o Tiktok Ads B\u1ea1n N\u00ean Bi\u1ebft"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p cho c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 2 lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.tiktok.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tiktok<\/a>\u00a0c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean Tiktok.<\/p>\n<p>Khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Tiktok \u0111\u1ec3 kinh doanh b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng cho s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n n\u00ean t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok. C\u00f3 bao nhi\u00eau lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean Tiktok v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0o?<\/p>\n<p>Trong n\u1ed9i dung b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y,\u00a0<strong>Ezmedia<\/strong>\u00a0s\u1ebd gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u cho c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n\u00a0<strong>2 lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok, ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t 2 lo\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n n\u00e0o cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_17 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-grey\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">N\u1ed9i dung b&agrave;i vi\u1ebft:<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: none;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"><\/i><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/baostar.pro\/2-loai-tai-khoan-quang-cao-tiktok-ads-ban-nen-biet\/#Tai_khoan_Tiktok_Ads_la_gi\" title=\"T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Tiktok Ads l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\">T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Tiktok Ads l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/baostar.pro\/2-loai-tai-khoan-quang-cao-tiktok-ads-ban-nen-biet\/#Tai_khoan_quang_cao_Tiktok_ca_nhan_Self-Serve\" title=\"T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n (Self-Serve)\">T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n (Self-Serve)<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/baostar.pro\/2-loai-tai-khoan-quang-cao-tiktok-ads-ban-nen-biet\/#Tai_khoan_quang_cao_Tiktok_doanh_nghiep_Agency\" title=\"T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok doanh nghi\u1ec7p (Agency)\">T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok doanh nghi\u1ec7p (Agency)<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/baostar.pro\/2-loai-tai-khoan-quang-cao-tiktok-ads-ban-nen-biet\/#Uu_va_nhuoc_diem_cua_hai_loai_tai_khoan_quang_cao_Tiktok\" title=\"\u01afu v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a hai lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok\">\u01afu v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a hai lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/baostar.pro\/2-loai-tai-khoan-quang-cao-tiktok-ads-ban-nen-biet\/#Nen_dung_loai_tai_khoan_nao_de_chay_quang_cao_Tiktok\" title=\"N\u00ean d\u00f9ng lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok\">N\u00ean d\u00f9ng lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/baostar.pro\/2-loai-tai-khoan-quang-cao-tiktok-ads-ban-nen-biet\/#Tam_ket\" title=\"T\u1ea1m k\u1ebft\">T\u1ea1m k\u1ebft<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2 id=\"ftoc-heading-1\" class=\"ftwp-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tai_khoan_Tiktok_Ads_la_gi\"><\/span><strong>T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Tiktok Ads l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean Tiktok, ch\u00fang m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec3u t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Tiktok Ads l\u00e0 g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Tiktok Ads l\u00e0 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch marketing, qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u kinh doanh \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u00fat kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u1eeb \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Tiktok \u0111\u1ebfn trang web b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng ho\u1eb7c gian h\u00e0ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 shop kinh doanh ho\u1eb7c doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\n<p>T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok hi\u1ec7n nay ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu chia l\u00e0m hai lo\u1ea1i:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n (Self-Serve)<\/li>\n<li>T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o doanh nghi\u1ec7p (Agency)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"ftoc-heading-2\" class=\"ftwp-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tai_khoan_quang_cao_Tiktok_ca_nhan_Self-Serve\"><\/span><strong>T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n (Self-Serve)<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n (Self-Serve)<\/strong>\u00a0l\u00e0 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ee9ng ra lo li\u1ec7u t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean Tiktok \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c n\u1ea1p ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7094\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7094\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7094 lazy-load-active\" src=\"https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-1.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1322px) 100vw, 1322px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-1.png 1322w, https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-1-300x188.png 300w, https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-1-1024x643.png 1024w, https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-1-768x482.png 768w\" alt=\"T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n (Self-serve)\" width=\"1322\" height=\"830\" data-src=\"https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-1.png\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-1.png 1322w, https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-1-300x188.png 300w, https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-1-1024x643.png 1024w, https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/1-1-768x482.png 768w\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7094\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n (Self-serve)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a Tiktok Ads. Hi\u1ec3u m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n th\u00ec n\u00f3 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ki\u1ec3u t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n \u201ct\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n tr\u00ean Tiktok. B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m t\u1eeb A \u0111\u1ebfn Z m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Tiktok.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"ftoc-heading-3\" class=\"ftwp-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tai_khoan_quang_cao_Tiktok_doanh_nghiep_Agency\"><\/span><strong>T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok doanh nghi\u1ec7p (Agency)<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Tiktok Ads th\u1ee9 hai l\u00e0\u00a0<strong>t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok doanh nghi\u1ec7p (Agency)<\/strong>. Lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Tiktok c\u1ea5p ri\u00eang cho c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ty v\u00e0 Agency l\u00e0m v\u1ec1 truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o nh\u1eb1m ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho nhu c\u1ea7u ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean Tiktok c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ch\u1ee7 shop ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p v\u1eeba v\u00e0 nh\u1ecf.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7095\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7095\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-7095 size-full lazy-load-active\" src=\"https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/2-16.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/2-16.jpg 800w, https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/2-16-300x175.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/2-16-768x448.jpg 768w\" alt=\"T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok doanh nghi\u1ec7p (Agency)\" width=\"800\" height=\"467\" data-src=\"https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/2-16.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/2-16.jpg 800w, https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/2-16-300x175.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/2-16-768x448.jpg 768w\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7095\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok doanh nghi\u1ec7p (Agency)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u00ean c\u00f4ng ty qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o (c\u00f4ng ty n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Tiktok \u1ee7y quy\u1ec1n) \u0111\u1ee9ng ra m\u1edf t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n, n\u1ea1p ti\u1ec1n, l\u00ean chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng marketing, theo d\u00f5i c\u00e1c b\u00e1o c\u00e1o v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a v\u1eadn h\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch lo cho b\u1ea1n. B\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1p tr\u00ean Tiktok, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng ra support v\u00e0 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft. Hi\u1ec3u m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n th\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi l\u00e0 b\u00ean trung gian gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00e0 thay b\u1ea1n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean Tiktok v\u1edbi ph\u00eda ch\u1ee7 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng Tiktok.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i cho vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 lo m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 t\u1eeb A \u0111\u1ebfn Z th\u00ec b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 cho c\u00f4ng ty truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c nhau t\u00f9y theo t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>Xem th\u00eam:\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/ezmedia.vn\/5-loai-hinh-quang-cao-tiktok\/\">5 Lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean Tiktok ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn<\/a><\/strong><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"ftoc-heading-4\" class=\"ftwp-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Uu_va_nhuoc_diem_cua_hai_loai_tai_khoan_quang_cao_Tiktok\"><\/span><strong>\u01afu v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a hai lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><\/td>\n<td><strong>T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n<\/strong><strong>(Self-Serve)<\/strong><\/td>\n<td><strong>T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok doanh nghi\u1ec7p<\/strong><strong>(Agency)<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"3\"><strong>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>T\u1ef1 qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean Tiktok<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>S\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Agency t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1eabu qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Agency s\u1ebd tri\u1ec3n khai quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch Tiktok Ads, qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 v\u1eadn h\u00ecnh t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Linh ho\u1ea1t h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ra m\u1eabu qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t gi\u00fap gia t\u0103ng \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok khi g\u1eb7p tr\u1ee5c tr\u1eb7c<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"3\"><strong>Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>T\u1ef1 lo li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 setup t\u1eeb A \u0111\u1ebfn Z<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c linh ho\u1ea1t trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n trao \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Agency v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Tiktok n\u1ebfu g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>T\u1ed1n ph\u00ed d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thu\u00ea t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o doanh nghi\u1ec7p<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i l\u00e2u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 Tiktok do ch\u01b0a h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Content qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb l\u1ed9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh c\u1eafp<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2 id=\"ftoc-heading-5\" class=\"ftwp-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nen_dung_loai_tai_khoan_nao_de_chay_quang_cao_Tiktok\"><\/span><strong>N\u00ean d\u00f9ng lo\u1ea1i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>M\u1ed7i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tiktok \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng &amp; marketing.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111a